  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program will implement a range of integrated activities to improve food security, access to health services, reduce drug abuse and improve disaster resilience of 16 program communities in Northern Shan. Establishment and strengthening of CBO&#x2019;s is an integral part of this program. Continued strengthening of local partner organizations (LPO&#x2019;s) (mostly church based) will shift in emphasis from general capacity building to equipment to achieve specific objectives. Especially there will be a role for local partner organizations in the area of prevention of drug abuse and address drug related problems.</narrative>
  </description>
